title: #2 Farm Weighting Adjustments
body:
We have 10 pools with total liquidity lower than $1.500.000 and 1x multiplier with means APR super very high (more than 250%)

I propose new multiplier 0.5x for this pools:

WSOTE - BNB
FRONT - BNB
HELMET - BNB
BTCST - BNB
BSCX - BNB
TEN - BNB
BALBT - BNB
UNFI - BNB
BLK - BNB
HARD - BNB

Rewards back to farms - 5.0

Racional thinking, this 5.0 flow back is NECESSARY to receive new farms. And for while it will slightly boost the existing farms.    

obs. Sorry for any english mistake, I'm not native
choices: Yes, Let's Be Prepare for New Pools!
